    "row": 32,
    "rowsha": "VnVz/vGtfDU9rg+A549hvu94BKvRudOs/HgsFHNudjU=",
    "originContent": "- State is stored in `./tailscale-state` next to the compose file, so node state and AWG settings survive container restarts and host reboots.",
    "translatedContent": "- 状态存储在 compose 文件旁的 `./tailscale-state` 中，因此节点状态和 AWG 设置能在容器重启及主机重启后保留。"
  },
