    "rowsha": "Q1ikOtr0MN1fnusclGxBZRcCW4UgK3YbZIJSP+JcXMY=",
    "originContent": "- If you are upgrading from the old bind mount `/var/lib/tailscale:/var/lib/tailscale`, copy the existing state first:",
    "translatedContent": "- 如果你是从旧的绑定挂载 `/var/lib/tailscale:/var/lib/tailscale` 升级，请先复制现有状态："
