    "originContent": "## Configuration Presets",
    "translatedContent": "## 配置预设"
  },
  {
    "row": 128,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 129,
    "rowsha": "KaYWb9YOv4yWX4pH0AAhlm+W72Qigx5X+FSX/iuFFYs=",
    "originContent": "| Goal | Example | Compatibility |",
    "translatedContent": "| 目标 | 示例 | 兼容性 |"
  },
  {
    "row": 130,
    "rowsha": "uOxIVVYHvGICEmxdtkLxHPiYFR+28qoZ0uKK6hnX5TI=",
    "originContent": "| --- | --- | --- |",
    "translatedContent": "| --- | --- | --- |"
  },
  {
    "row": 131,
    "rowsha": "Tyunrm6SYJ/daDwYg8LYuxaldwHQBYVzJi5tzJHDass=",
    "originContent": "| Basic junk traffic | `tailscale awg set '{\"jc\":4,\"jmin\":64,\"jmax\":256}'` | Works with standard Tailscale peers |",
    "translatedContent": "| 基础垃圾流量 | `tailscale awg set '{\"jc\":4,\"jmin\":64,\"jmax\":256}'` | 适用于标准 Tailscale 节点 |"
  },
  {
    "row": 132,
    "rowsha": "ELnvKRBeENGsVW+BuEomgo6g9QmT3bWvQJgqU4tMHDE=",
    "originContent": "| Junk traffic + signatures | `tailscale awg set '{\"jc\":2,\"jmin\":64,\"jmax\":128,\"i1\":\"<b 0x40><r 12>\"}'` | Works with standard Tailscale peers |",
    "translatedContent": "| 垃圾流量 + 签名 | `tailscale awg set '{\"jc\":2,\"jmin\":64,\"jmax\":128,\"i1\":\"<b 0x40><r 12>\"}'` | 适用于标准 Tailscale 节点 |"
  },
  {
    "row": 133,
    "rowsha": "BTDa2yH9Hc02uE+QKotNJSeRT3zvUMPzfWcoBPbe6pM=",
    "originContent": "| Handshake masquerading | `tailscale awg set '{\"s1\":10,\"s2\":15,\"s3\":8,\"s4\":0}'` | All AWG nodes must use the same `s1`-`s4` |",
    "translatedContent": "| 握手伪装 | `tailscale awg set '{\"s1\":10,\"s2\":15,\"s3\":8,\"s4\":0}'` | 所有 AWG 节点必须使用相同的 `s1`-`s4` |"
  },
  {
    "row": 134,
    "rowsha": "0EzSj9OZ9lWbDFmLoXeN1fn3Gi2pExBcdhKcWFPv8HI=",
    "originContent": "| Full masquerading | `tailscale awg set '{\"s1\":10,\"s2\":15,\"s3\":8,\"s4\":0,\"h1\":{\"min\":100000,\"max\":200000},\"h2\":{\"min\":300000,\"max\":350000},\"h3\":{\"min\":400000,\"max\":450000},\"h4\":{\"min\":500000,\"max\":550000}}'` | All AWG nodes must use the same `s1`-`s4` and `h1`-`h4` |",
    "translatedContent": "| 全面伪装 | `tailscale awg set '{\"s1\":10,\"s2\":15,\"s3\":8,\"s4\":0,\"h1\":{\"min\":100000,\"max\":200000},\"h2\":{\"min\":300000,\"max\":350000},\"h3\":{\"min\":400000,\"max\":450000},\"h4\":{\"min\":500000,\"max\":550000}}'` | 所有 AWG 节点必须使用相同的 `s1`-`s4` 和 `h1`-`h4` |"
  },
  {
    "row": 135,
    "rowsha": "nzWdQCdy6twCETJn8TuD58UEpKW1Otf5t3fzPzVuti8=",
    "originContent": "| Full masquerading + signatures | `tailscale awg set '{\"s1\":10,\"s2\":15,\"s3\":8,\"s4\":0,\"h1\":{\"min\":100000,\"max\":200000},\"h2\":{\"min\":300000,\"max\":350000},\"h3\":{\"min\":400000,\"max\":450000},\"h4\":{\"min\":500000,\"max\":550000},\"i1\":\"<b 0xc0><r 32><c><t>\"}'` | `i1`-`i5` may differ per node; `s1`-`s4` and `h1`-`h4` must match |",
    "translatedContent": "| 全面伪装 + 签名 | `tailscale awg set '{\"s1\":10,\"s2\":15,\"s3\":8,\"s4\":0,\"h1\":{\"min\":100000,\"max\":200000},\"h2\":{\"min\":300000,\"max\":350000},\"h3\":{\"min\":400000,\"max\":450000},\"h4\":{\"min\":500000,\"max\":550000},\"i1\":\"<b 0xc0><r 32><c><t>\"}'` | `i1`-`i5` 可因节点而异；`s1`-`s4` 和 `h1`-`h4` 必须匹配 |"
  },
  {
    "row": 136,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 137,
    "rowsha": "JTRAOy83hSgAaUvmv6EXj/8TpBBRvn1/lvdgOrJpY+g=",
    "originContent": "## Parameter Reference",
    "translatedContent": "## 参数参考"
  },
  {
    "row": 138,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 139,
    "rowsha": "7HX0M/G9mAd95wzrVGvwvSpsdz3PFOolzWScuIPoAhU=",
    "originContent": "- `jc` with `jmin` and `jmax`: junk packet count and size range.",
    "translatedContent": "- `jc` 与 `jmin` 和 `jmax`：垃圾包数量及大小范围。"
  },
  {
    "row": 140,
    "rowsha": "W4sQaAMExPotG+YSKm9fZmAUTleXmCiBwaD6auxYsQo=",
    "originContent": "- `i1`-`i5`: optional CPS (Custom Protocol Signature) chain for custom protocol-mimicking packets.",
    "translatedContent": "- `i1`-`i5`：可选的 CPS（自定义协议签名）链，用于自定义协议模拟包。"
  },
  {
    "row": 141,
    "rowsha": "vre34egHu86kWXvKxjmhNLi9nT3EGReh7aB0z1IukTw=",
    "originContent": "- `s1`-`s4`: handshake padding or prefix fields; all AWG nodes must match.",
    "translatedContent": "- `s1`-`s4`：握手填充或前缀字段；所有 AWG 节点必须匹配。"
  },
  {
    "row": 142,
    "rowsha": "GCx8aQ1bLy+COxyefK1TKGgMgfgcUBTKOOzlmjzqBXk=",
    "originContent": "- `h1`-`h4`: header field ranges in the form `{\"min\": low, \"max\": high}`; either set all four or none. The ranges must not overlap, and all AWG nodes must match.",
    "translatedContent": "- `h1`-`h4`：头字段范围，格式为 `{\"min\": 低值, \"max\": 高值}`；必须全部设置或全部不设置。范围不能重叠，且所有 AWG 节点必须匹配。"
  },
  {
    "row": 143,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
  },
  {
    "row": 144,
    "rowsha": "dm1+r9jp26kOFHhr9/Mn5zxOWlc5JjC67/1P9Yul4Wk=",
    "originContent": "Very large junk counts or long signature chains increase latency and bandwidth usage.",
    "translatedContent": "非常大的垃圾包数量或较长的签名链会增加延迟和带宽使用。"
  },
  {
    "row": 145,
    "rowsha": "47DEQpj8HBSa+/TImW+5JCeuQeRkm5NMpJWZG3hSuFU=",
    "originContent": "",
    "translatedContent": ""
